# Engine release artifacts under public/{berserk,plentychess,viridithas,stockfish}/
# are intentionally trackable so deployed GPL binaries and their corresponding
# source archives/manifests cannot be hidden by ignore rules. Keep generated
# precompressed sidecars ignored; they are rebuilt for dist deploys.
